en_text:
Lady Delphine, the alliance fleet
will soon enter the zone of engagement.
jp_text: 艦長　戴冠式の場にギルド戦艦
google_translated: Guild battleship at the captain crowned place

en_text:
Enemy's maximum firing range, 12 miles!
Our rate of descent is too fast!
jp_text: つの始まりとするなら
google_translated: If it is the beginning of one

en_text:
Maintain descent! Drop to range
where line-of-sight combat is possible.
jp_text: 今が来るべき時だとするなら
google_translated: If it is time to come now

en_text:
Once Alvis Hamilton and
the fourth Mysterion arrive,
jp_text: 永远を掴む、その果てには
google_translated: Grab the Energy, that's the end

en_text:
Maintain present speed!
Join the battle line!

jp_text: すごい人がこの船にへ載ってたんだな
google_translated: A great person was on this ship

en_text:
Blow a path through those tentacles!
Give it everything you've got!
jp_text: 当たり前だ　副長だぞ
google_translated: It is a matter of course

jp_text: 周囲の聴音　厳にせよ
ギルドのお姉ちゃんと昔ちょっとあってな
google_translated: There is a long time with the guild's sister

jp_text: 下方　無音航行中のウルバヌスです

en_text:
Because I told you
to get out?!
google_translated: Did you come to be sinked

en_text:
So, this is the edge
of this world, eh?

jp_text: 現在シルヴァーナとウルバヌスのみです

en_text:
This would have been even more enjoyable
if Dio were here, though...

Stand by torpedoes!
Set fuses for 12 seconds!
jp_text: その短針音によりエグザイルを探します
google_translated: Look for an exile by its short hand sound

jp_text: 私たちはそれまでにエグザイルを発見し 捕獲しなければなりません
google_translated: We have to discover and capture exiles by then

en_text:
All hands, evacuate to bow of ship!
Here she comes!
jp_text: しかし短針音だけでは　目標の確認が...
google_translated: However, the target of the goal is checked by only short hand sounds ...

jp_text: これはデュシスが捕捉したエグザイルの駆動音です
google_translated: This is the driving sound of the Exile captured by Dusys

en_text:
See? You're even more
handsome now.
jp_text: わたしはシルヴァーナで指揮をとります
google_translated: I will command you in Sylvana

en_text:
Armor-piercing jet-propelled array!
Full spread! Fire!
jp_text: いやな予感があたったよ

en_text:
Don't stop! Keep going forward, even if
you have to drag the things with us!
jp_text: グランドストリームに行くぞ
google_translated: I will go to the ground stream

en_text:
I heard the Captain's voice
from inside Delphine's ship!
jp_text: ギルドのマエストロ・デルフィーネに対し 降伏を迫ったようなものです
google_translated: It is like approaching the surrender of the guild Maestro Delphine

jp_text: グランドストリーム内では　音響弾裝を行うため
google_translated: In order to perform acoustic bullets in the ground stream

en_text:
Claus! I see a light!
Bearing, 2 o'clock!
jp_text: 私はあなた方全員が 総力をつくしてくれることを期待します
google_translated: I hope all of you will make a total of power

jp_text: この作戦が成功するかいなかは すべて乗員の努力にかかっています
google_translated: All this strategy is successful and it depends on the effort of the occupant

en_text:
No way am I gonna
red-out this time!
jp_text: これで給金にはつきますね
アルはどうなってしまうんですか

en_text:
All hands, stand by to abandon ship.
Stand down from battle stations.

jp_text: ギルドに対抗するには　エグザイルが必要なの
google_translated: An exile is required to compete with the guild

jp_text: クラウス　クラウスいる？

en_text:
The Captain...
What did he say?

What lies in the furthest
reaches of the sky?

The blessed breath
which nurtures life.

What lies in the furthest
depths of memory?

jp_text: ここにいりゃ　腕のいい整備師になるだろうにな
google_translated: It will be a good maintenance teacher who is here.

en_text:
I'll always be your first officer.
Now and forever.

jp_text: ここちょいきつくしめすぎ

en_text:
What do you call all those drops
coming out of your eyes, then?

Inside Exile, we found
our dads' Vanship.
jp_text: これは生きて帰った証だよ
google_translated: This is a proof that he was alive

en_text:
Let's give them some
time alone, okay?
jp_text: ラヴィもタチアナさんの時も
google_translated: Ravi is also time of Tachiana

en_text:
Our dads kept trying,
right up to the end.
jp_text: たまごは食べるくせに

en_text:
To us, there was no
Anatoray or Disith.
jp_text: いいもわるいもないよ

en_text:
...we're going to start building
a world without fighting. Together.
jp_text: 僕がずっとここにいたいな
google_translated: I want to be here for a long time

jp_text: 最初の一発目は　ここだ
google_translated: The first one shot is here

en_text:
...in a town where the white
flowers bloom, but now...
jp_text: 魚雷を撃つ方も責任重大だな
google_translated: If you shoot torpedo, it is also a responsibility

en_text: When everything goes off into the endless skies,
jp_text: グランドストリームに突入

en_text: ...where does it go to, I wonder?
jp_text: やっぱ重ねないほうがよかったじゃないですかね
google_translated: It would not be better not to have a lot

en_text:
The place of peace
we are searching for,

When everything goes off
into the endless skies,

If you are going
to travel the skies,

jp_text: わたしは翼になりたい
google_translated: I want to be a wing

en_text:
One day, I promise
that I will have...
jp_text: いつか　きっと持つから

en_text:
...no matter how strong
the wind may be.
